# Maintenance Schedule

## Daily Tasks
- **Deployment Monitoring**: Check deployment status
- **Error Monitoring**: Review error logs
- **Performance Monitoring**: Check Core Web Vitals
- **Security Monitoring**: Review security alerts

## Weekly Tasks
- **Dependency Updates**: Check for dependency updates
- **Security Scans**: Run security vulnerability scans
- **Performance Review**: Analyze performance metrics
- **Backup Verification**: Verify backup integrity

## Monthly Tasks
- **Code Review**: Review code quality and standards
- **Documentation Update**: Update project documentation
- **Performance Optimization**: Identify optimization opportunities
- **Security Audit**: Conduct security audit

## Quarterly Tasks
- **Major Updates**: Plan major feature updates
- **Architecture Review**: Review system architecture
- **Scalability Assessment**: Assess system scalability
- **Compliance Review**: Review compliance requirements

## Dependency Management
```bash
# Weekly dependency check
npm audit
npm outdated
npm update

# Security updates
npm audit fix
npm audit fix --force

# Major version updates
npm-check-updates -u
```

## Performance Monitoring
- **Core Web Vitals**: Monitor LCP, FID, CLS
- **Bundle Size**: Track bundle size changes
- **Load Times**: Monitor page load times
- **Error Rates**: Track error rates

## Security Maintenance
- **Vulnerability Scans**: Regular security scans
- **Access Review**: Review access permissions
- **Secret Rotation**: Rotate sensitive secrets
- **Security Updates**: Apply security patches

## Database Maintenance
- **Backup Verification**: Verify backup integrity
- **Performance Tuning**: Optimize database performance
- **Index Maintenance**: Maintain database indexes
- **Data Cleanup**: Clean up old data

## Infrastructure Maintenance
- **SSL Certificate**: Monitor SSL certificate expiration
- **Domain Renewal**: Monitor domain expiration
- **CDN Optimization**: Optimize CDN configuration
- **Monitoring Setup**: Ensure monitoring is active

## Code Quality Maintenance
- **Linting**: Run linting checks
- **Type Checking**: Verify TypeScript types
- **Test Coverage**: Maintain test coverage
- **Code Review**: Regular code reviews

## Documentation Maintenance
- **README Updates**: Keep README current
- **API Documentation**: Update API docs
- **Deployment Guides**: Update deployment guides
- **Troubleshooting**: Update troubleshooting guides

## Emergency Procedures
- **Incident Response**: Define incident response procedures
- **Rollback Procedures**: Define rollback procedures
- **Contact Information**: Maintain contact information
- **Escalation Procedures**: Define escalation procedures

## Maintenance Checklist
- [ ] Dependencies updated
- [ ] Security scans completed
- [ ] Performance monitored
- [ ] Backups verified
- [ ] Documentation updated
- [ ] Code reviewed
- [ ] Tests passing
- [ ] Monitoring active
- [ ] SSL certificates valid
- [ ] Emergency procedures documented
